nodes.text: Lehibe was a female Human who served in the Republic Army during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the reconstituted Sith Empire. She was stationed aboard Carrick Station, where she distributed equipment.

Lehibe appeared in the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic, released by BioWare in 2011, as a Corellia Equipment Commendations Vendor on Carrick Station, though she was later relabeled as a Level 50 Equipment Commendations Vendor. With the release of Game Update 4.0 on October 20, 2015, she was removed from the game along with the rest of the Equipment Commendations Vendors.
